name: BOOBY
description: Our team of brilliant bird brained developers created this project with one goal in mind: to share the Boobies among the community. Boobies are stronger together, and instead of flying throughout the sea, lets go take our Booby blue feet beyond, our unique and quirky team of rocket scientists has been working to send Boobies to the moon.You can expect a wild ride, lots of heart PUMPING moments, and most importantly, lots of boobies! Do you have what it takes to become a Booby?
